{"id":9791,"title":"Epizootic hemorrhagic disease in a yak.","abstract":"Épizootie hémorragique chez un yack. Une infection par le virus de la maladie épizootique hémorragique du cerf a été diagnostiquée chez un yack âgé de 3 ans. Le yack présentait des signes de tremblements intermittents, de dysphagie, de lésions ulcératives buccales, d’entérite hémorragique, de tachypnée et de thrombocytopénie. Le diagnostic postmortem a confirmé l’épizootie hémorragique (sérotype 2) à l’aide de la technique RT-PC. Les résultats bruts et histopathologiques étaient conformes à l’épizootie hémorragique signalée chez d’autres espèces.(Traduit par Isabelle Vallières).Epizootic hemorrhagic disease virus (EHDV) infection was diagnosed in a 3-year-old yak. The yak had signs of intermittent tremors, dysphagia, oral ulcerative lesions, hemorrhagic enteritis, tachypnea, and thrombocytopenia. Postmortem diagnostics confirmed EHDV (serotype 2) using reverse-transcriptase polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR). Gross and histopathological results were consistent with EHDV reported in other species. ","date":"2014-04-01","categories":"Animal Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24688138","annotations":[{"name":"Dysphagia","weight":0.894932,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dysphagia"},{"name":"Tachypnea","weight":0.884338,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tachypnea"},{"name":"Polymerase chain reaction","weight":0.869327,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polymerase_chain_reaction"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Virus","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virus"},{"name":"Epizootic","weight":0.775712,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epizootic"},{"name":"Thrombocytopenia","weight":0.775064,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thrombocytopenia"},{"name":"Histopathology","weight":0.76942,"wi